---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About This Guide"
  description="Who runs this Ace Combat 8: Wings of Theve guide, how we source information, and how often it's updated."
>
  <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'About' }]} />
  <article class="container article">
    <span class="eyebrow">Editorial transparency</span>
    <h1>About This Guide</h1>

    <p>
      This is an independent, unofficial fan guide to <strong>ACE COMBAT 8: WINGS OF THEVE</strong>.
      We are not affiliated with, endorsed by, or operated by Bandai Namco Entertainment Inc.
      or Bandai Namco Aces Inc. All trademarks, aircraft names, and game assets referenced
      belong to their respective owners.
    </p>

    <h2>How we source information</h2>
    <p>
      Every claim on this site is either sourced directly from Bandai Namco's official
      channels (press releases, the official game site, State of Play/Game Awards trailers,
      Steam and PlayStation Store listings) or clearly labeled as an editor estimate pending
      official confirmation. Pages that contain estimated data — like aircraft stat ratings
      before launch — carry a visible
      <span class="badge badge--estimate" style="margin: 0 4px;">Est.</span>
      badge so it's never confused with confirmed information.
    </p>

    <h2>How often this is updated</h2>
    <p>
      We're tracking every official Bandai Namco announcement in the run-up to the
      October 2, 2026 launch. Aircraft and edition pages show a "Last updated" date so you can
      see at a glance whether information reflects the latest official reveal. After launch,
      we shift to verifying every editor estimate against real gameplay.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Spotted something outdated or incorrect? We'd rather fix it fast than leave it wrong —
      reach out via the contact details on our social channels linked in the footer.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .article {
    padding: 56px 0 80px;
    max-width: 720px;
  }
  .article p { font-size: 0.98rem; }
</style>
